{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:1",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنشَقَّتۡ",
      "translation": "(1) When the sky has split [open]",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:2",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ",
      "translation": "(2) And has listened [i.e., responded][1888] to its Lord and was obligated [to do so]",
      "footnotes": "[1888]- It will have heard Allāh's command and will have inclined immediately to compliance and willing obedience."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:3",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَإِذَا ٱلۡأَرۡضُ مُدَّتۡ",
      "translation": "(3) And when the earth has been extended[1889]",
      "footnotes": "[1889]- i.e., stretched flat and spread out."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:4",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَلۡقَتۡ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتۡ",
      "translation": "(4) And has cast out that within it[1890] and relinquished [it]",
      "footnotes": "[1890]- Of the dead and all else buried therein."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:5",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ",
      "translation": "(5) And has listened [i.e., responded] to its Lord and was obligated [to do so] –",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:6",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدۡحٗا فَمُلَٰقِيهِ",
      "translation": "(6) O mankind, indeed you are laboring toward your Lord with [great] exertion[1891] and will meet it.[1892]",
      "footnotes": "[1891]- i.e., striving throughout your life until you meet your Lord, hastening toward death.\n[1892]- i.e., you will find all that you intended and accomplished awaiting you in the Hereafter. Another meaning is \"And will meet Him [i.e., your Lord]\" and be recompensed in full by Him."
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:7",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ",
      "translation": "(7) Then as for he who is given his record in his right hand,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:8",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَسَوۡفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابٗا يَسِيرٗا",
      "translation": "(8) He will be judged with an easy account",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:9",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورٗا",
      "translation": "(9) And return to his people in happiness.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:10",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهۡرِهِۦ",
      "translation": "(10) But as for he who is given his record behind his back,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:11",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَسَوۡفَ يَدۡعُواْ ثُبُورٗا",
      "translation": "(11) He will cry out for destruction",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:12",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَيَصۡلَىٰ سَعِيرًا",
      "translation": "(12) And [enter to] burn in a Blaze.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:13",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِيٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورًا",
      "translation": "(13) Indeed, he had [once] been among his people in happiness;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:14",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ",
      "translation": "(14) Indeed, he had thought he would never return [to Allāh].",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:15",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بَلَىٰٓۚ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرٗا",
      "translation": "(15) But yes! Indeed, his Lord was ever, of him, Seeing.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:16",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلشَّفَقِ",
      "translation": "(16) So I swear by the twilight glow",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:17",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّيۡلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ",
      "translation": "(17) And [by] the night and what it envelops",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:18",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا ٱتَّسَقَ",
      "translation": "(18) And [by] the moon when it becomes full",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:19",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَتَرۡكَبُنَّ طَبَقًا عَن طَبَقٖ",
      "translation": "(19) [That] you will surely embark upon [i.e., experience] state after state.[1893]",
      "footnotes": "[1893]- i.e., various stages, both in this life and in the Hereafter."
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:20",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَمَا لَهُمۡ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ",
      "translation": "(20) So what is [the matter] with them [that] they do not believe,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:21",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": "obligatory",
      "sajdah_number": 13,
      "text": "وَإِذَا قُرِئَ عَلَيۡهِمُ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ لَا يَسۡجُدُونَۤ۩",
      "translation": "(21) And when the Qur’ān is recited to them, they do not prostrate [to Allāh]?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:22",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ يُكَذِّبُونَ",
      "translation": "(22) But those who have disbelieved deny,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:23",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱللَّهُ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَا يُوعُونَ",
      "translation": "(23) And Allāh is most knowing of what they keep within themselves.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:24",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَبَشِّرۡهُم بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ",
      "translation": "(24) So give them tidings of a painful punishment,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 589,
      "verse_key": "84:25",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 236,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ أَجۡرٌ غَيۡرُ مَمۡنُونِۭ",
      "translation": "(25) Except for those who believe and do righteous deeds. For them is a reward uninterrupted.",
      "footnotes": ""
    }
  ]
}